'''гласность''' (glásnost’) ''f''

# [[public]], [[publicity]]
# [[openness]]
# [[glasnost]]
#: Soviet policy of the 1980s. [[w:Mikhail Gorbachev|Mikhail Gorbachev]] began to promote a policy of openness in public discussions about current and historical problems. The policy was termed glasnost [publicity, openness]. This would then be coupled with [[perestroika]].

